# ArgoCore Global AI Rules
- Architecture: Modular approach.
- Core logic (Auth, UI components, Database connections) goes into `/core`.
- Domain-specific logic goes into dedicated modules: `/modules/ecommerce`, `/modules/saas`, `/modules/portfolio`.
- NEVER mix domain logic. E-commerce code must not leak into Portfolio or SaaS modules.
- Use Server Components by default. Use 'use client' only when hooks/state are needed.
- Write clean, abstraction-focused code to minimize token usage.
- Read referenced `.md` files carefully before generating code.